.PP
All macros expand to a call to Logger, where \fILevel\fR is taken from the macro name, or from the first argument in the case of the \fI?LOG\fR macro. Location data is added to the metadata as described under the \fImetadata/0\fR type definition.

.PP
The call is wrapped in a case statement and will be evaluated only if \fILevel\fR is equal to or below the configured log level.

.PP
